S.FORM: Paridrayan i Pingtung a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Paridrayan. u kasalumaluma' nu Paridrayan sa, 229 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 733 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 718 ku tademaw, pakalatu 98 . u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 15 ku tademaw, pakalatu 2 . u kasabinacadan, Paiwan 95 , Rukai 1 , Bunun 1 , zumazuma 1 . malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan
